The objective of this study is to assess the efficacy and safety of different doses of Creon Immediate Release (IR) in comparison to Creon(R) 25,000 Delayed Release/Gastro-Resistant (DR/GR) in subjects with Pancreatic Exocrine Insufficiency (PEI) due to Cystis Fibrosis (CF).

